@startuml fig-component-view
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontName Microsoft YaHei
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam dpi 200

title 零售物品智能识别系统 — 开发运行视图（组件交互图）

actor "商超管理员" as Admin
actor "小程序用户" as Customer

node "前端开发机" {
  component [retail-admin-pro\n(Vue3 + Vite + Element Plus)\n:5173] as FrontAdmin
}

node "微信平台" {
  component [retail-customer\n(微信小程序)] as MiniApp
}

node "应用服务器" {
  component [retail-server\n(Spring Boot 3.3 + Java 21)\n:8080] as Backend
  component [retail-ai\n(FastAPI + Uvicorn)\n:8000] as AIService
}

database "MySQL 8.x\n(retail_db)\n:3306" as DB
database "Redis 8.x\n:6379" as Cache
component [USB 摄像头\n(DirectShow)] as Camera

Admin --> FrontAdmin : 浏览器访问
Customer --> MiniApp : 微信客户端

FrontAdmin --> Backend : HTTP/JSON\n(Vite 代理 /api/*)
MiniApp --> Backend : HTTPS/JSON\n(wx.request /api/applet/*)

Backend --> DB : JDBC\n(MyBatis-Plus)
Backend --> Cache : Lettuce\n(推荐流缓存)
Backend --> AIService : HTTP/JSON\n(RestTemplate /api/ai/*)

AIService --> Camera : OpenCV\n(cv2.VideoCapture)

note right of Backend
  **定时巡检**
  CameraScanScheduler
  每5分钟调用
  /api/ai/recognize/shelf/batch
end note

note bottom of AIService
  **AI 能力端点**
  · 摄像头探测/预览/流
  · 中心点识别 (Top-K)
  · 批量货架识别
  · 文本关键词检索
end note

@enduml
